theorem Topology.isOpen_of_isClosed_of_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hclosed : IsClosed A) (hP3 : Topology.P3 A) :
    IsOpen A := by
  have hInt_subset : interior A ⊆ A := interior_subset
  have hA_subset : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior A := by
    have : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure A) := hP3
    simpa [hclosed.closure_eq] using this
  have hEq : interior A = A := by
    apply Set.Subset.antisymm
    · exact hInt_subset
    · exact hA_subset
  simpa [hEq] using isOpen_interior

theorem Topology.P2_of_dense_interior {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (h : Dense (interior A)) : Topology.P2 A := by
  dsimp [Topology.P2]
  intro x hx
  have : x ∈ (Set.univ : Set X) := by
    simp
  simpa [h.closure_eq, interior_univ] using this
